# speckit Plan: richards_sudoku

## Phases
1) Foundations (MVP alignment) — COMPLETE
- Set up project layout (src/, tests/) with PyQt6 entrypoint and config.
- Implement core model: board state, candidates, undo/redo (board + pencil), timer, stats.
- Implement solver/validator (backtracking + constraints) for standard 9x9; seedable generator producing unique solvable puzzles; difficulty placeholder.
- Build PyQt6 UI shell: main window, grid widget, keyboard/mouse + keyboard-only controls, light/dark (Arial, min font 6pt).
- Persistence: versioned JSON save/load with atomic writes; prompt for path.
- Basic flows: new game (standard), play, save/load, pencil marks, undo/redo, timer display.
- Smoke tests: pytest + pytest-qt for render/select/undo/redo; unit tests for solver/generator/persistence round-trip.

2) Variants & Assistance (Beta alignment)
